      <title>拜登官员同意权衡学生债务减免的变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/education-department-agrees-to-hold-another-student-debt-cancellation-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在民主党议员和有影响力的倡导团体的压力下，美国教育部同意就替代学生债务减免计划的提议举行另一次规则制定会议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/education-department-agrees-to-hold-another-student-debt-cancellation-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 19:49:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国亨特警告三月份预算减税空间有限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/uk-s-hunt-warns-limited-room-for-tax-cuts-in-march-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在彭博社报道英国财政监管机构本周向财政部提交了有限的数字后，英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特警告说，他在即将到来的预算中减税的空间有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/uk-s-hunt-warns-limited-room-for-tax-cuts-in-march-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 19:39:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登为何要严厉打击银行透支费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/bank-overdraft-fees-why-biden-is-cracking-down-on-lenders-explained</link>
      <description><![CDATA[消费者权益倡导者长期以来一直抱怨美国银行和信用合作社向弱势客户收取过高的透支费用。近年来，在拜登政府金融监管机构的压力下，各大银行已采取自愿措施减少透支费收入。但白宫希望走得更远，并提出限制措施，可能会更大幅度地削减大银行从透支费中赚取的数十亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/bank-overdraft-fees-why-biden-is-cracking-down-on-lenders-explained</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 19:19:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>史蒂夫·施瓦茨曼 (Steve Schwarzman) 是佳士得入主白宫失败的华尔街捐助者之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/schwarzman-ackman-gave-to-christie-s-failed-white-house-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石集团 (Blackstone) 的史蒂芬·施瓦茨曼 (Stephen Schwarzman) 和潘兴广场资本管理公司 (Pershing Square Capital Management) 的比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman) 是华尔街捐助者之一，他们为前新泽西州州长克里斯·克里斯蒂 (Chris Christie) 反对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 竞选共和党提名的失败活动提供了资金支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/schwarzman-ackman-gave-to-christie-s-failed-white-house-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 18:40:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>扎克伯格在参议院儿童安全听证会上即兴道歉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/zuckerberg-offers-impromptu-apology-at-child-safety-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，在紧张的证词中，Meta Platforms Inc. 首席执行官马克·扎克伯格 (Mark Zuckerberg) 站在挤满人的参议院听证室前，直接向在社交媒体平台上遭受性剥削的儿童的家人道歉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/zuckerberg-offers-impromptu-apology-at-child-safety-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 18:33:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Coinbase 及其首席执行官为支持加密货币的政客准备“战争基金”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/coinbase-coin-and-ceo-armstrong-prep-war-chest-for-pro-crypto-politicians</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于布莱恩·阿姆斯特朗的两名最强大的竞争对手入狱或可能很快就会入狱，布莱恩·阿姆斯特朗无疑已成为数字资产行业最强大的领导者。他的崛起发生在一个有趣的时刻：美国大选竞选季开始，他的公司将其描述为“加密货币历史上最重要的一次”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/coinbase-coin-and-ceo-armstrong-prep-war-chest-for-pro-crypto-politicians</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 18:09:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国挫败了中国针对路由器的黑客行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/us-disrupted-chinese-hacking-operation-that-targeted-routers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦调查局和司法部官员周三表示，美国的一项行动破坏了中国政府支持的黑客攻击行动，其中间谍劫持了一个大型设备网络，以水利设施和电网等为目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/us-disrupted-chinese-hacking-operation-that-targeted-routers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 17:03:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta、X、TikTok 首席执行官因儿童网络安全问题遭到参议员批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/meta-x-tiktok-ceos-face-us-senate-on-protecting-kids-online</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，五个社交媒体平台的领导人因“未能”保护网上儿童免受性掠夺者和心理健康问题的侵害而受到美国立法者的警告，并被迫支持新的立法以实施控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/meta-x-tiktok-ceos-face-us-senate-on-protecting-kids-online</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:36:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国寻求通过修改贸易计划来结束北爱尔兰僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/uk-plans-to-ease-gb-n-ireland-trade-flows-to-restore-stormont</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国公布了一项减少从英国流向北爱尔兰的货物贸易摩擦的计划，此举预计将说服民主统一党结束对该地区权力下放政府的两年抵制，尽管该计划尚未达成重大协议彻底修改英国脱欧规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/uk-plans-to-ease-gb-n-ireland-trade-flows-to-restore-stormont</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:18:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
